00:58:03,814 --> 00:58:05,049
There?

767
00:58:05,149 --> 00:58:07,051
Are you sure, miss?

768
00:58:07,151 --> 00:58:09,820
I'm quite sure, thank you.

769
00:58:13,057 --> 00:58:14,659
All off?

770
00:58:14,759 --> 00:58:16,594
All off.

771
00:58:17,294 --> 00:58:19,029
Off.

772
00:58:28,072 --> 00:58:29,640
