825
01:02:05,823 --> 01:02:07,992
Um... gelato?

826
01:02:08,092 --> 01:02:10,060
Gelato.

827
01:02:11,996 --> 01:02:13,230
Thank you.

828
01:02:13,330 --> 01:02:14,699
Grazie.

829
01:02:14,799 --> 01:02:17,334
Signorina, il resto.

830
01:02:17,434 --> 01:02:19,369
Oh. Grazie.

